      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PEAKY AVENGER (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (20.16) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning nine races. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to her name from 10 starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. PLAYBACK (8) comes off an average run last start when sixth at this track over 350m behind Paw Vada (20.46) in a Grade 4/5. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and six minor placings to his credit. Bold showing expected. JUSTIFIED JIM (3) was below best at his last start when 7th at Warragul following a second place finish (24.69) at Sale two back. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Should be about the money. MAN OF COURAGE (2) warrants respect following a recent placing at big odds.",
